INPUT PARAMETERS

PARAMETER VALUE
Genotype filename gwaspoly-genotype-tetra-ACGT.tbl
Phenotype filename gwaspoly-phenotype-tuber_shape.tbl
Significance level 0.05
Correction method Bonferroni
Trait
GWAS model Structure
Filtering TRUE
MIND Filter (Individual with missing genotype) 0.1
GENO Filter (SNPs with missing genotype) 0.1
MAF Filter (Minor allele frequency) 0.01
HWE Filter (Hardy-Weinberg test) 1e-10
